# Corporation API

## Path Prefix

All corporation API endpoints use: `/ganb/api/corporation/v1/`

The `HttpClient` prepends this automatically — pass only the relative path from
`/ganb/api/corporation/v1/` onward (e.g. `/transfer/request`, not the full URL).

## Endpoints (v1.8.0 scope)

### Account / Balance / Transaction

| Resource | Method | Path |
|---|---|---|
| Accounts list | GET | `/accounts` |
| Balance | GET | `/accounts/balances` |
| Transactions | GET | `/accounts/transactions` |

### Virtual Accounts (振込入金口座)

| Resource | Method | Path |
|---|---|---|
| VA list | GET | `/virtual-accounts` |
| VA create | POST | `/virtual-accounts` |
| VA status update | PATCH | `/virtual-accounts/{vaId}` |
| VA transactions | GET | `/virtual-accounts/{vaId}/transactions` |

### Single Transfers (振込依頼)

| Resource | Method | Path |
|---|---|---|
| Create transfer | POST | `/transfer/request` |
| Transfer status | GET | `/transfer/status` |
| Transfer result | GET | `/transfer/request-result` |
| Transfer fee | POST | `/transfer/transferfee` |
| Cancel transfer | POST | `/transfer/cancel` |

### Bulk Transfers (総合振込依頼)

| Resource | Method | Path |
|---|---|---|
| Create bulk transfer | POST | `/bulktransfer/request` |
| Bulk transfer status | GET | `/bulktransfer/status` |
| Bulk transfer result | GET | `/bulktransfer/request-result` |
| Bulk transfer fee | POST | `/bulktransfer/transferfee` |
| Cancel bulk transfer | POST | `/bulktransfer/cancel` |

> NOTE: GMO Aozora uses verb-based paths (`/transfer/request`, `/bulktransfer/cancel`)
> NOT REST-style resource paths (`/transfers/{id}`). Never use the REST-style pattern.

## Field Types

- `amount`: always string (`"5800"`) — use `parseAmount()` → bigint
- `accountId`: string, 12–29 digits
- `applyNo`: 16-digit numeric string (振込申請番号)
- `nextItemKey`: pagination token (string), present when more records exist
- `resultCode`: `'1'`=完了, `'2'`=未完了, `'8'`=期限切れ

## Pagination Pattern

Use the async iterator for transaction listing:

```typescript
for await (const tx of client.corporation.transactions.iterate({
  accountId,
  dateFrom: '2026-04-01',
  dateTo: '2026-04-30',
})) {
  // automatic pagination via nextItemKey
}
```

Never implement manual `while (nextItemKey)` loops in application code.

## Transfer pollResult (production helper)

Both single and bulk transfers can return `resultCode === '2'` (still processing).
Use the built-in `pollResult` helper instead of polling manually:

```typescript
// Single transfer (up to 99 items)
const result = await client.corporation.transfers.pollResult(
  { accountId, applyNo },
  { intervalMs: 3_000, timeoutMs: 60_000 },
);

// Bulk transfer (up to 9,999 items)
const result = await client.corporation.bulkTransfers.pollResult(
  { accountId, applyNo },
  { intervalMs: 60_000, timeoutMs: 7_200_000 },
);
```

`pollResult` throws `GmoAozoraTimeoutError` when `timeoutMs` is exceeded.

## Error Handling

Map API error codes from the response body to typed error classes.
Always include the API error code, message, and `requestId` in the error.
